description:
Bring Fun Moments to Your Friends with CamCool.

CamCool takes snapshots and make videos with dozens of real-time filters. 
It brings more than 30 Unique styles of filters to you from funny to artsy, all with funny, innovative, and beautiful design. Intuitive controls allow you tap, swipe or pinch at anytime to adjust enhancement while recording.

--- Features --- 
+ Four-leaf clover shaped interface 
+ Real-time effects for snapping pictures and recording video 
+ Tap and swipe to move the filter center on the photo or video 
+ Pinch and zoom to focus on a key part of the photo or video 
+ Front & back facing camera support 
+ Creative filter corner makes amazing style 
+ Share photos and videos with friends through Instagram, Facebook, Twitter, Flickr, SMS or e-mail 
+ Export video and image to Mac/PC via iTunes 

--- Basic Effects --- 
1-5: Squeeze, Stretch, Block-face, Light Tunnel, Mirror 
6-10: Swirl, Pixellate, Cross Hatching, Cross Hatching 2, Vignette 
11-15: Thermal Camera, Color Invert, Sepia, Sketch, Edge 
16-20: Toon, Blur, Brightness, Contrast, Gamma 
21-25: Sharpen, Night Vision, Bright & White, Emboss, Posterize

--- Unique effects --- 
26-30: Shockwave, Water, Mosaic, Dream Vision, Polar Pixellate 
31-32: Dilation, Erosion

Download NOW and see how FUN it is!
